'''漢堡王'''（{{lang-en|Burger King}}，簡稱BK）是全球大型連鎖[[速食|速食]]企業。自1953年它的前身「速食漢堡王」餐廳開幕以來，餐點便是以漢堡、薯條、軟性飲料、奶昔和甜點為主。餐廳在被[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[邁阿密|邁阿密]]的加盟店收購後，1954年改名為「[[漢堡王|漢堡王]]」，並開始豐富它的菜單，例如1957年創立[[華堡|華堡]]三明治，也逐漸加入雞肉、魚肉和蔬食等非牛肉單品，如沙拉和無肉漢堡。此外，它也供應早餐餐點和[[冰吸|冰吸]]（Icee）、果汁與瓶裝水等飲品選擇。不同於其他飲食業者著重於擴展全球版圖，漢堡王結合當地特色，推出符合地方口味和文化或宗教信仰的產品。為刺激買氣，漢堡王每隔一段時間便會販賣季節限定的特別漢堡單品，或開發全新產品，以開拓短期或長期銷量。然而，這些產品和服務並非全為成功的政策；例如，1993年，漢堡王引進以特別晚餐拼盤為賣點的限量[[桌邊服務|桌邊服務]]，但未引起討論、增加銷售，最終以失敗收場。

== 歷史 ==
=== 漢堡與主餐 ===
[[File:Burger_king_whopper.jpg|thumb]]
1953年，漢堡王的前身「速食漢堡王」（Insta-Burger King）在[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[傑克遜維爾_(佛羅里達州)|傑克遜維爾]]開業，以漢堡、薯條、軟性飲料和甜點為餐點主軸<ref name="Jakle-1">{{cite book |title=Fast Food: Roadside Restaurants in the Automobile Age |first1=John A. |last1=Jakle |first2=Keith A. |last2=Sculle |last3=Pappas |publisher=JHU Press |year=1999 |edition=1<sup>st</sup> |pages=116–117 |isbn=080186920X |url= http://books.google.com/?id=0nYcgnWKWXgC&pg=PA119&lpg=PA119&dq=burger+king+specialty+sandwiches+-nutrition+-subservient+-fries |accessdate=2009-06-15 |quote=Mathew Burns of Long Beach, California, and Kieth g. Kramer, Burn's stepson and owner of a Daytona Beach, Florida drive in, founded Insta-Burger King, Burger King's predecessor.}}</ref>。速食漢堡王在1954年被加盟商[[詹姆斯·麥拉摩爾|詹姆斯·麥拉摩爾]]和[[大衛·艾傑頓|大衛·艾傑頓]]收購，改名「漢堡王」，並持續開發它的核心餐點、烹飪技術及設備。1957年，麥拉摩爾和艾傑頓發明了漢堡王的招牌餐點「[[華堡|華堡]]」，意圖在眾多漢堡業者中樹立品牌特色。華堡是重約4盎司（110公克）的漢堡，內夾有生菜、番茄、美奶滋、酸黃瓜和番茄醬，訂價29[[美分|美分]]。它主打大口飽足、用料實在的高水準，在平均15美分的平價漢堡市場脫穎而出<ref name="NRN-Carlino">{{cite news |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m3190/is_n32_v30/ai_18609870/ |title=BK co-founder McLamore dead at 70 |last=Carlino |first=Bill |date=1996-08-19 |work=Nation's Restaurant News |accessdate=2010-01-25 |archive-date=2011-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111116155552/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m3190/is_n32_v30/ai_18609870/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Whopper">{{cite press release |url=http://www.bison.com/press_BurgerKing_02282002 |title=Burger King Celebrates As The Whopper Turns 45 |publisher=Burger King Corporation |date=2002-02-08 |accessdate=2007-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080112003433/http://www.bison.com/press_BurgerKing_02282002 |archive-date=2008-01-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。華堡很快地成為漢堡王的旗艦餐點，也延伸出許多華堡系列單品。漢堡王亦多次在華堡的食材上做小幅調整，包括1970年代早期將以芝麻漢堡麵包取代白麵包，以及1980年代中期的調整[[漢堡排|漢堡排]]（patty）尺寸<ref name="nrn-whopper & bundles">{{cite news |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m3190/is_v21/ai_4686664/ |title=Burger King chief plays peacemaker |last=Romero |first=Peter J. |date=1987-02-16 |work=Nation's Restaurant News |publisher=BNet.com |accessdate=2009-10-19 |archive-date=2008-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915165628/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m3190/is_v21/ai_4686664 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自推出以來，華堡已然成為漢堡王的代名詞，也是漢堡王廣告宣傳的重點<ref name="wsj-whopper">{{cite news |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB120244090812952965-email.html |title=Hey, No Whopper on the Menu?! |last=Vranica |first=Suzanne |date=2008-02-08 |work=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]] |pages=B3 |location=New York city |accessdate=2009-10-23 |archive-date=2009-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090417022111/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB120244090812952965-email.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。漢堡王甚至將旗下[[販售亭|販售亭]]風格的分店取名為「[[華堡吧|華堡吧]]」（Whopper Bars）<ref name="ap-whopper">{{cite news |url=http://www.usatoday.com/money/industries/food/2009-03-09-whopper-bar_N.htm |title=Burger King to open first Whopper Bar |date=2009-03-09 |work=USA Today |agency=Associate Press |accessdate=2009-10-21 |archive-date=2009-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090822095123/http://www.usatoday.com/money/industries/food/2009-03-09-whopper-bar_N.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 營養 ==
1983年，漢堡王推出[[沙拉吧|沙拉吧]]，首度嘗試開拓健康飲食市場。這項突破獲得小幅迴響，但加盟店紛紛對此投資的高營運成本和低利潤報酬表示不滿<ref name="nrn-salad bar">{{cite news |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m3190/is_v18/ai_3298622/ |title=Results mixed from Burger King's salad bar |last=Edwards |first=Joe |date=1984-06-04 |work=Nation's Restaurant News |publisher=BNet.com |accessdate=2009-10-27 |archive-date=2005-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050505013621/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m3190/is_v18/ai_3298622/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其中一項單品「皮塔沙拉」在成功達到促進早餐銷量的目的後，很快地便從沙拉吧下架<ref name="nrn-fail">{{cite news |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m3190/is_v18/ai_3403640/ |title=New products: why some succeed, others fail – fast food restaurants |last=Forman |first=Charles |date=1984-10-27 |work=Nation's Restaurant News |publisher=BNet.com |accessdate=2009-10-27 |archive-date=2005-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050321023827/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m3190/is_v18/ai_3403640/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1987年，漢堡王推出預先包裝的沙拉單品，包括[[主廚沙拉|主廚沙拉]]和[[田園沙拉|田園沙拉]]等口味選擇，逐漸取代沙拉吧<ref name="nrn-1987 salads">{{cite news |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m3190/is_21_38/ai_n6048404/?tag=content;col1 |title=Burger chains toss packaged salads |last=Van Warner |first=Rick |date=1987-06-08 |work=Nation's Restaurant News |publisher=BNet.com |accessdate=2009-10-29}}</ref>。1990年，漢堡王和[[保羅·紐曼|保羅·紐曼]]的「Newman's Own」公司協議合作，引進新的沙拉產品，並選用該公司的沙拉醬作為佐醬<ref name="funding-newmans">{{cite web |url=http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/Newmans-Own-Inc-Company-History.html |title=Newman's Own, Inc. |work=FundingUniverse.com |accessdate=2009-10-27 |archive-date=2012-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510213435/http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/Newmans-Own-Inc-company-History.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2004年，漢堡王又再度改良它的沙拉陣容，推出火烤沙拉系列產品<ref name="usat-salads">{{cite news |url=http://www.usatoday.com/money/industries/food/2004-01-13-burger-king-steak_x.htm |title=Burger King goes bun-less, adds high-protein salads |date=2004-01-13 |work=USA Today |accessdate=2011-01-23 |archive-date=2006-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060117132250/http://www.usatoday.com/money/industries/food/2004-01-13-burger-king-steak_x.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。新產品提供烤蝦或烤雞二種選擇，並革新性地將熱溫的肉食和沙拉冷品分開包裝，讓沙拉產品外觀、口感都更顯清爽<ref name="sbm-shrimp">{{cite web |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-128867436.html |title=Low-carb diets spark growing interest in salads |last=Kramer |first=Lauren |date=2005-02-01 |work=Seafood Business Magazine |accessdate=2009-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105071831/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-128867436.html |archive-date=2012-11-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在美國，沙拉一般在店外預先製作完成，並提供二種肉食搭配選擇以及「Ken's Foods」品牌沙拉醬。在美國以外的地區，各國的沙拉產品都有不同的食材和配方，但其銷售對象皆主要是女性及具有健康意識的消費者。<ref name="bk-delight">{{cite press release|url=http://www.farsons.com/page.asp?n=newsdetails&i=2583 |title=Burger King introduces the King Delight line |publisher=[[Simonds_Farsons_Cisk|Simonds Farsons Cisk]] |date=2004-07-27 |accessdate=2009-11-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710225611/http://www.farsons.com/page.asp?n=newsdetails&i=2583 |archivedate=2011-07-10 }}</ref><ref name="een-larange">{{cite web|url=http://edinburghnews.scotsman.com/ViewArticle.aspx?articleid=2467807 |title=Change is on the menu for a quick fix |last=Howden |first=Sarah |date=2003-10-06 |work=Edinburgh Evening News |publisher=The Scotsman.com |accessdate=2009-11-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110616030306/http://edinburghnews.scotsman.com/ViewArticle.aspx?articleid=2467807 |archivedate=2011-06-16 }}</ref>

